---
title: Chinese Hoisin-Glazed Pork with Broccoli & Coconut Rice
description: Every element of this recipe is a winner, from the hoisin-glazed pork to the more-ish coconut rice and tender-crisp veggies. So if you're looking for an easy midweek dinner that's big on flavour on low on fuss, this one's for you.
